      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Run once to create the Data Tables\n\nClick **Execute workflow**. This creates the two Data Tables the Email Assistant needs:\n`email_queue` and `reply_sessions`.\n\nSafe to re-run — if a table already exists it is reused, not duplicated. The main workflow references both tables **by name**, so no manual re-pointing is needed.",
